node.text:
We're kicking off our first est film production with a momentous Malvern Home renovation by @dohertydesignstudio from est magazine issue #35.
.
Tapping into its rich architectural past and 1980s new wave bones, @dohertydesignstudio have skilfully commandeered an epic journey to reinvent this Melbourne family home. An original 1980's design by architect Peter McIntyre. .
.
Experience the entire home via the link in profile or read the full feature in est magazine issue #35. .
.
Design @dohertydesignstudio
Building design @arialexander
Builder @north_building_group 
Styling @heathernetteking 
Florals and assitant styling @rachelpolivkastylist 
Art consultant @gb.art.consulting 
Landscape design @benscott_design 
Videography @richardlipp.studio
Words @meganmayrawson
Art @tompolo @liamsnootle @anyapesce @oocaleb @davidjamesgriggs @christianthompsonartist #leekyoung-hwa 
Furniture & Objects @domoaustralia @lightlydesign @loomtowels @fenton_and_fenton @abode_living @moderntimesau @ajarfurniture @lamarzoccohomeau

node.text:
Great land. Great architecture. Great living. In an est exclusive, we feature three unique films by Rob Mills Architecture & Interiors (RMA). Australian-based RMA’s latest project, a ground-breaking residence in Byron Bay incorporates Mill’s signature use of drama, curves, lines, light and a reflection of the qualities of the land.
.
View all three films via link in profile.
.
Videography @collider__
Creative Direction | Design @robmillsarchitects

node.title: Exclusive | The latest architectural project by Rob Mills

node.text:
INTERIORS | Dendê Duratex House 
​.
@nildojose_arquitetura designed this concept residence in Brazil's São Paulo with the brief to use a range of Duratex materials, including skirting boards, Laminex and vinyl flooring.
.
Spanning a living room, kitchen, dining room, master suite and a courtyard with a tree in the middle, the concept home taps into a serene sensory experience through the  harmonious material application. ​
​.
​Design @nildojose_arquitetura
​Photography @marcoantoniofoto
​.
https://www.estliving.com/

​.
​Explore one of @olsonkundig's latest projects, a West Hollywood home with views across L.A. – from the San Gabriel Mountains to the Pacific Ocean.
​.
​The home takes in the L.A. cityscape while dissolving boundaries between the interiors and outdoor pool area. 
​.
​Design @olsonkundig
​Photography @aaronleitz and @nic.lehoux
​.
​https://www.estliving.com/

​.
​Rombo IV by @taller_aragones is located in Mexico City's Bosques de las Lomas neighbourhood, reflecting the design firm's minimalist and Modernist approach to residential architecture.

node.text:
DESIGNER INTERVIEW | Celebrating 21 Years of Mim Design 
​.
​"The moment you choose to say in your career, 'I actually want to enjoy the process', and enjoy a client relationship or enjoy working with another creative, you get a better result. When everyone is invested, you work on delivering an amazing project, but you also really enjoy the experience. Collaboration enables me to enjoy what I do."
​– Mim Fanning
​.
​In anticipation of the release of Mim Fanning’s retrospective book ‘Works’, we sat down with the Melbourne interior designer to recognise 21 years of her practice, @mimdesignstudio, and how it’s shaped the Australian design landscape.
​.
​Read more about Mim's retrospective 'Works' recognises this milestone – and her biggest feats and learnings – on estliving.com – link in profile. 
​.
​Design @mimdesignstudio 
​Photography @tfadtomferguson, @peterclarkephoto, @blachford & @davekulesza 
​.
​https://www.estliving.com/21-years-mim-design/

node.text:
ARCHIPRODUCTS DESIGN AWARDS | Nominate Your Favourite Design Product in 2021
​.
​For the first time, we're proud to announce we're the official Australian media partner of the 2021 @archiproducts Design Awards.
​.
​Hosted by architecture and design resource Archiproducts, the awards puts design on a global stage to recognise, reward and celebrate excellence across a broad range of categories.
​.
​An impressive list of more than 60 judges across 14 categories includes @harrynuriev,  @chrissa.amuah, @rossana_orlandi, @bobby, @eyeswoon, @quincocesdrago, @giorgiodona and @hesrawe.
​.
​Entries for the ADAs must be submitted by the 16th September 2021, with both longlisted products and winners announced between October and November 2021.
​.
Pictured: Anim bathtub by @salvatori_official, 2020 Archiproducts Design Award winner.
​.
​https://www.estliving.com/archiproducts-design-awards/
